  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 15th level, as a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Swift-Actions\">swift action</a>&nbsp;once per day, you can take 2 points of temporary&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Ability-Score-Damage\">ability damage</a>&nbsp;to one of your ability scores and add a temporary +2 inherent bonus to any other ability score. This bonus lasts for a maximum of 1 hour per&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/sorcerer\">sorcerer</a>&nbsp;level or until you choose to prematurely dismiss it (a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Free-Actions\">free action</a>), during which time the temporary&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Ability-Score-Damage\">ability damage</a>&nbsp;cannot be healed by any means. After this effect ends, you can heal the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Ability-Score-Damage\">ability damage</a>&nbsp;normally.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>At 20th level, you can use this ability twice per day.</li>\n</ul>"
    },
